reviewText: Tape was exactly as described - works great and very good movie! Excellent seller!

While this is movie is not in CD form, I still was able to enjoy it. It arrived quite quickly and except for a few jumps (common in old films), it was easy and most enjoyable to watch. I am looking forward to purchasing more items (especially with Jack Lord in them) and I thank Amazon for their great service. I highly recommend Amazon to anyone purchasing just about anything.
